text: Antarctodomus is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Species== Species within the genus Antarctodomus include: * Antarctodomus okutanii Numanami, 1996 * Antarctodomus thielei (Powell, 1958) ==References== Category:Buccinidae
title: Antarctodomus
